data.title: Billy Wingrove on LinkedIn: Thanks for all your birthday messages but unfortunately it’s not…
data.meta_description: Thanks for all your birthday messages but unfortunately it’s not technically my birthday today. On every bit of ID I have including my birth certificate states… | 14 comments on LinkedIn
data.text: “Yes guys!” we only had Billy Wingrove in our studios yesterday! Really enjoyed hosting this conversation for our clients to gain a better understanding of how YouTube creators are having a real world impact on culture and beyond. Billy is a great example of an innovative creator who consistently delivers fresh, high quality and relevant content which is enabling advertisers and agencies to reach new audiences in extremely engaged environments. A master at delivering what his audience wants in this expanding world of AV.....oh and what a nice human being as well! Top man Billy, excited for you in 2023. #youtube #youtubecreator #creatoreconomy #creators
